---

<section id="use-cases" class="py-24 bg-navy-900/50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        Built For <span class="text-gradient">Growing Teams</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        If your operation feels noisy, leaky, or constrained by manual work — you're not alone. Here's how we help.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- Agencies -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div>
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-teal-400/10 text-teal-400 text-sm font-medium rounded-full mb-4"
          >
            Agencies
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
            From Pipeline Chaos to Predictable Client Acquisition
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
            Agencies live and die by their pipeline. When inboxes are noisy, follow-ups slip, and your best leads go cold because no one had time to respond. We build systems that ensure every qualified opportunity gets the attention it deserves.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Automated lead qualification so you only talk to decision-makers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Persistent follow-up sequences that don't let deals slip</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>CRM hygiene that gives you real visibility into your pipeline</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-600/20 to-electric-600/20 rounded-2xl blur-2xl"
          >
          </div>
          <div
            class="relative bg-navy-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8"
          >
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-400/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-2">The Problem</p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Great leads going cold because your team is buried in admin work and can't follow up fast enough.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Professional Services -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="relative">
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-electric-600/20 to-teal-600/20 rounded-2xl blur-2xl"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="relative bg-navy-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8"
            >
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-electric-400/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-electric-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-2">The Problem</p>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">20+ hours a week lost to data entry, document processing, and manual follow-ups that could be automated.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-electric-400/10 text-electric-400 text-sm font-medium rounded-full mb-4"
          >
            Professional Services
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
            From Operational Bottlenecks to Scalable Delivery
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
            Consultancies, law firms, accounting practices — you bill for expertise, not admin work. Yet your team spends hours on data entry, scheduling, and chasing updates. We automate the operational overhead so you can scale delivery without scaling headcount.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-electric-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Document processing and data syncing on autopilot</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-electric-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Client communication workflows that never miss a beat</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-electric-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Tool integration so nothing falls through the cracks</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Growth-Stage Companies -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div>
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-teal-400/10 text-teal-400 text-sm font-medium rounded-full mb-4"
          >
            Growth-Stage Companies
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">
            From Manual Workflows to Automated Infrastructure
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
            You've outgrown your scrappy early-stage processes but can't afford enterprise solutions or big ops teams. We build the automation infrastructure that lets you operate like a company twice your size — without the overhead.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-400">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Systems that scale with you, not against you</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Reactivate dormant leads your CRM forgot about</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Engineering-grade reliability, not duct-tape solutions</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-600/20 to-electric-600/20 rounded-2xl blur-2xl"
          >
          </div>
          <div
            class="relative bg-navy-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8"
          >
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-400/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-2">The Problem</p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Hitting an invisible ceiling — growth is capped not by effort, but by operational capacity that can't keep up.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
